
# 🚀 ElectroLaunch

A lightning-fast application launcher built with **Electron**, designed to streamline your workflow by providing instant access to applications, files, and websites through an elegant, minimalist interface.

---

## ✨ Features

- ⚡ **Instant Search & Launch**  
  Find and start any application in milliseconds with intelligent fuzzy search.
- 🔗 **Smart Shortcuts**  
  Easily create custom shortcuts for apps, files, folders, and websites.
- 🗑️ **Simple Management**  
  Add, edit, or remove shortcuts through a clean, intuitive UI.
- 📊 **Usage Analytics** *(privacy-friendly)*  
  See your most-used apps — all data stored locally.
- 🎨 **Customizable Themes**  
  Switch between light, dark, and system themes for visual comfort.
- ⌨️ **Keyboard Navigation**  
  Navigate entirely via keyboard for maximum productivity.
- 🔄 **Automatic Updates**  
  Stay up to date with the latest features and improvements automatically.

---

## 📥 Installation

### Pre-Built Binaries

Download the latest version for your platform:

- 🪟 [**Windows (64-bit)**](https://github.com/fathuur7/electro-launch/releases/latest/download/ElectroLaunch-Setup-Windows-x64.exe)
- 🍎 [**macOS**](https://github.com/fathuur7/electro-launch/releases/latest/download/ElectroLaunch-darwin-x64.dmg)
- 🐧 [**Linux (.deb)**](https://github.com/fathuur7/electro-launch/releases/latest/download/electro-launch_amd64.deb)
- 🐧 [**Linux (.AppImage)**](https://github.com/fathuur7/electro-launch/releases/latest/download/ElectroLaunch-linux-x86_64.AppImage)

---

## 🧑‍💻 Development Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/fathuur7/electro-launch.git

# Navigate into the project directory
cd electro-launch

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start the app in development mode
npm start
```

---

## 📁 Folder Structure

```
.
├── main.js         # Main Electron process
├── preload.js      # Optional preload script
├── index.html      # Main HTML UI
├── renderer.js     # UI logic
├── src/
│   └── styles/     # CSS styles
└── package.json
```

---

## 🏗️ Build from Source

```bash
# For Windows
npm run build:win

# For macOS
npm run build:mac

# For Linux
npm run build:linux

# Build for all platforms
npm run build
```

---

## 🧩 Tech Stack

- **[Electron](https://www.electronjs.org/)** — Cross-platform desktop app framework
- **[Electron Forge](https://www.electronforge.io/)** — All-in-one toolchain for Electron development
- **Node.js Core Modules**
  - `fs` — File system
  - `path` — Path utilities
  - `child_process` — Spawn processes
  - `os` — OS-level utilities

